        <description>&lt;i&gt;Repossed&lt;/i&gt; is a puzzle board game. The player's task is to direct the worm to go through the exit block 'E' by the appropriate shifting blocks 'O'. In each turn the worm moves by 15 regions in designated direction until it encounters an obstacle causing change of the current path. Changing the path the worm always tries to move according to a clockwise direction. The player may move up to 15 fields in each turn. Apart from directing the worm to exit area the player must prevent the worm from entering the deadly glowing squares.</description>
